      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I've been reading up on HIIT training and I'm a bit confused about the biochemistry. Can you explain the process of how lactic acid (lactate) is actually produced in muscle tissue during high-intensity intervals, and how the body manages to clear it out during the recovery phase?",
